summary: CONSUMER CALLED COMPLAINING ABOUT HAVING PROBLEMS WITH BACK TAIL LIGHT. ALSO STATED THAT WHILE DRIVING THE VEHICLE THE BACK COVER FOR THE TAIL LIGHT POP OFF WHICH CAUSE DAMAGE TO THE VEHICLE. DEALER WAS CONTACTED AND STATED THAT THEY NEVER HEARD OF THAT PROBLEM AND THAT THE VEHICLE WARRANTY WON'T COVER IT.    PH  *DT
